title: #194 - William & Chelsea Osman
description: On this episode of the H3 Podcast we are joined by YouTuber, inventor, beanie enthusiast and facial hair haver- William Osman and his incredibly caretaker Chelsea Osman! Together we discuss their brush with COVID, science and teaching, bones human or otherwise, and mountains of meat aka meat mountains, and a whole lot more!!!
itunes:author: Ethan Klein
